com.ephesoft.dcma.kvfinder.service

Interface KVFinderService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    KVFinderServiceImpl

    public interface KVFinderService
    This is a service to search for key value based extraction. Api will first search the key pattern and then search the value pattern on the basis of location.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
    See Also:
    KVFinderServiceImpl

        inputFilePath - String absolute path for image file used for ocring.

        DCMAException - if any of the input is not valid.
